channel.title: Unforeseen Consequences - Stuck on pipe
channel.description:
While derping around in Unforeseen Consequences today, in the room where the Houndeye smashes through the window and begins attacking you, I got stuck on a pipe as I was battling it. Even without the Houndeye there, I can't get out.

Thanks. :slight_smile:
